name: The Lady of LaFerla Manor
description:
One of the three maidens of La Ferla Manor. The Lady is the caretaker of the home, making sure the house is orderly and tidy, everything in its right proper place.

Shot on location at the home of Dominic La Ferla in Torrance, California.

See the body painting in motion at: https://youtu.be/1I_bx_68bQU

model: Teri Wyble
body paint and photography by: Roustan (bodypainter.com)
